defaultwww.datagat
defaulte
defaultway.phe.org.uk
default) which allows access to resources across the 140 legacy sites that previously supported the full range of our products.  All legacy sites will be migrated to a new single site.  We are currently working 
defaultwith our users to identify their needs and with the Government Digital Service on the design of the new site. 
default&#xa0;
defaultPHE will work closely with 
defaultt
defaulthe National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE) to ensure access to high quality public health evidence
default and advice.  NICE is responsible for setting quality standards for health, social care and public health. PHE will ensure full integration of evidence resources from the NICE evidence service into t
defaulthe PHE Knowledge service.  Our K
defaultnowledge service will als
defaulto include evidence and guidance from other sources such as the National Screening Committee and 
defaultthe 
defaultJoint Committee on Vaccination and immunisation.
