defaultd breakdo
defaultwn of PHE’s workforce.  
defaultThese are set out in Annexes C &amp; D. 
defaultWe employ a wide range of scientific, technical, professional and medical staff, on an equal
defaultly diverse range of activities.  
defaultThese range from specialised roles in reference laboratories, high 
defaultcontainment facilities, pathology testing for the NHS and vaccine production to the delivery of screening programmes and public health support to
default Local Authorities and the NHS.  
defaultWe would be happy to provide further details of our activities and their impac
defaultt. 
defaultI hope this further informati
defaulton is of help to the committee.  
defaultWe stand ready to provide any further material you may find helpful.  I would like to thank the Committee for the opportunity to talk to you about what PHE does, and look forward to continui
defaultng our conversation.
